# Project Building Steps
## Requirements

1.  read text files from a directory.
2.  run based on a keyboard shortcut
3.  paste text into any program including the terminal.
4.  have a GUI for selecting text based on a shortcut
5.  have a GUI for editing text
6.  have a GUI for adding text
7.  if a shortcut is mentioned in mustache notation {{ var_name }} that file will also be retrieved.
8.  Avoid recurrsion/infinite loops.

## Features

1.  Override the default directory based on an enviromental variable


## Steps
1. Read the first file in the .texpander directory and copy its contents to the clipboard
2. Do the above when hitting a shortcut.
3. Have a GUI that lists the files in that directory.
